WEBVTT

00:00:45.738 --> 00:00:50.359
MY NAME IS BRONNIE TAIT. B. R. O. DOUBLE N. I. E.,

00:00:50.359 --> 00:00:52.196
T. A. I. T..

00:00:52.269 --> 00:00:55.084
I AM INTERVEWING MISTER WACLAW JABLONSKI,

00:00:55.084 --> 00:00:58.172
W. A. C. L. A. W.,

00:00:58.209 --> 00:01:02.586
J. A. B. L. O. N. S. K. I..

00:01:03.201 --> 00:01:06.558
TODAY IS MAY NINETEEN, NINETEEN NINETY SEVEN,

00:01:06.583 --> 00:01:11.432
WE ARE IN MELBOURNE, AUSTRALIA, AND THE INTERVIEW WILL BE CONDUCTED IN YIDDISH.

00:01:29.816 --> 00:01:31.650
kenst mir zogn dayn nomen?

00:01:32.702 --> 00:01:34.856
haynt, der hayntiker?

00:01:33.618 --> 00:01:35.210
haynt, yo.

00:01:35.351 --> 00:01:38.349
der nomen, Yablonski Vadslav.

00:01:38.928 --> 00:01:42.804
un v- vos iz geven dayn nomen ven du host geboyrn geven?

00:01:42.810 --> 00:01:45.167
Yankev Yosef Kurts.

00:01:45.577 --> 00:01:48.356
un far vos hostu es oysgetoysht?

00:01:48.615 --> 00:01:50.938
az ikh zol mikh oprateven,

00:01:51.247 --> 00:01:53.857
ikh zol vern a goy, a polak.

00:01:53.829 --> 00:01:56.135
un ven hos- ven hot dos geshen?

00:01:56.343 --> 00:02:02.632
in yor toyznt nayn hundert eyn un fertsik hob ikh geendert dem nomen.

00:02:03.735 --> 00:02:07.099
un anshtots tsu geyn hobn a yidishn pasport,

00:02:07.099 --> 00:02:10.631
hob ikh gehat a poylisher ken-karte.

00:02:10.687 --> 00:02:13.719
un vu hostu genumen di karte?

00:02:14.417 --> 00:02:19.221
in fun a polak velkher iz krank gevezn un er iz geshtorbn,

00:02:19.867 --> 00:02:21.957
hob ikh gekrign zayn

00:02:21.977 --> 00:02:25.026
karte, ken-karte, azoy hot es geheysn.

00:02:25.098 --> 00:02:27.742
emetser hot gegebn tsu dir, ober?

00:02:26.752 --> 00:02:31.977
yo ah, vayl der polak iz oykh geven di untererdishe bavegung,

00:02:32.118 --> 00:02:34.593
hot di familye gegebn mir

00:02:34.650 --> 00:02:36.652
dem pasport zaynem.

00:02:37.164 --> 00:02:39.757
ikh vel fregn mer shpeter.

00:02:40.235 --> 00:02:42.845
ven hostu geboyrn geven?

00:02:42.615 --> 00:02:43.538
ikh?

00:02:43.307 --> 00:02:43.926
yo.

00:02:43.998 --> 00:02:48.987
ikh bin geboyrn gevorn, dem akht un tsvontsikstn februar

00:02:49.162 --> 00:02:51.991
toyznt nayn hundert tsen.

00:02:52.385 --> 00:02:54.016
un vi alt bistu yetst?

00:02:55.457 --> 00:02:59.687
oy! yetst bin ikh shoyn mer vi a akh- zibn un akhtsik.

00:03:00.418 --> 00:03:02.556
un vu hostu geboyrn geven?

00:03:02.257 --> 00:03:03.753
in Varshe.

00:03:04.164 --> 00:03:06.347
oyf dem Niske Gas,

00:03:06.347 --> 00:03:08.512
zeks un zekhtsik.

00:03:09.294 --> 00:03:12.073
ven di mame iz nokh geshlofn bay nakht.

00:03:14.036 --> 00:03:16.612
vos iz dayn, der nomen fun dayn foter?

00:03:16.787 --> 00:03:17.949
Doved.

00:03:17.985 --> 00:03:19.549
David, DAVID.

00:03:19.706 --> 00:03:22.738
un vu hot er geboyrn geven?

00:03:23.520 --> 00:03:29.043
er iz gevezn in Obershlezyen in a shtetele.

00:03:29.043 --> 00:03:32.238
nor vi es heyst gedenk ikh - in Obershlezyen.

00:03:32.600 --> 00:03:34.180
un ven?

00:03:34.286 --> 00:03:35.820
veys ikh nisht.

00:03:36.395 --> 00:03:37.621
un dayn muter?

00:03:37.863 --> 00:03:41.202
mayn muter iz geboyrn gevorn in Ukov.

00:03:41.205 --> 00:03:43.376
veys ikh nisht.

00:03:42.960 --> 00:03:43.882
di nomen?

00:03:45.086 --> 00:03:47.260
Perl, hot zi geheysn.

00:03:47.260 --> 00:03:49.856
nor vi azoy zi hot geheysn der nomen,

00:03:49.929 --> 00:03:52.010
UNK veys ikh oykh nisht.

00:03:52.010 --> 00:03:53.130
fun zeydn.

00:03:53.726 --> 00:03:55.003
ikh gedenk nisht.

00:03:55.633 --> 00:03:57.804
du host gehat shvester o brider?

00:03:58.063 --> 00:04:03.373
zi hot gehat zeks shvestern zenen zey gevezn. keyn brider iz nisht geven.

00:04:03.497 --> 00:04:04.909
zeks meydlekh.

00:04:05.589 --> 00:04:06.883
un dayn foter?

00:04:07.293 --> 00:04:08.705
mayn foter?

00:04:08.154 --> 00:04:09.951
er hot gehat brider un shvester?

00:04:08.829 --> 00:04:11.113
ah, mayn foter hot gehat

00:04:11.113 --> 00:04:14.139
brider, shvester,

00:04:14.533 --> 00:04:17.632
er hot gehat a groyse familye der foter mayne.

00:04:18.228 --> 00:04:19.820
un du host gehat

00:04:19.820 --> 00:04:21.328
shvester o brider?

00:04:21.536 --> 00:04:22.520
ver?

00:04:22.076 --> 00:04:22.830
du.

00:04:22.565 --> 00:04:23.606
ikh?

00:04:23.780 --> 00:04:26.238
tsvey shvesters hob ikh gehat.

00:04:26.497 --> 00:04:28.246
nomen? di eltste?

00:04:28.657 --> 00:04:30.845
eyne hot geheysn

00:04:30.969 --> 00:04:34.912
Maria, un di andere Sara.

00:04:35.627 --> 00:04:38.372
un ven hot Sara geboyrn geven?

00:04:38.850 --> 00:04:42.388
Sara iz geven di eltste tokhter,

00:04:42.478 --> 00:04:47.754
zi iz geboyrn gevorn in yor toyznt nayn hundert tsvelf.

00:04:48.165 --> 00:04:49.071
un Maria?

00:04:49.278 --> 00:04:52.516
un Maria iz geboyrn gevorn in yor

00:04:52.516 --> 00:04:55.787
toyznt nayn hundert zibetsn.

00:04:57.952 --> 00:05:01.881
ikh vel yetst fregn dir frage fun

00:05:01.881 --> 00:05:05.540
dayn lebn fir di krig.

00:05:06.002 --> 00:05:08.376
vos gedenkstu fun

00:05:08.870 --> 00:05:11.720
l- dayn lebn in Varsheve

00:05:11.720 --> 00:05:12.932
far di krig?

00:05:14.692 --> 00:05:15.817
koydem,

00:05:15.958 --> 00:05:19.969
bin ikh gegangen, mayn, in a kheyder gelernt.

00:05:21.763 --> 00:05:23.436
du host geglaykht der kheyder?

00:05:23.439 --> 00:05:25.790
in a kheyder, ir veyst vos taytsh kheyder?

00:05:26.370 --> 00:05:30.938
aza religyeze shule iz es.

00:05:32.114 --> 00:05:34.715
nakher hob ikh gelernt

00:05:34.993 --> 00:05:37.721
veltlekher lerers,

00:05:38.115 --> 00:05:40.154
in a shule

00:05:40.154 --> 00:05:45.466
in Varshe bay nakht, a ovnt kursn heyst es.

00:05:46.097 --> 00:05:47.661
ver hot dir gelernt?

00:05:48.020 --> 00:05:49.621
ver se hot mikh gelernt?

00:05:49.621 --> 00:05:52.557
di ovnt kursn iz gevezn a shule

00:05:52.577 --> 00:05:55.409
velkhe hot gelernt tsu di Yisha, Yidishe

00:05:55.409 --> 00:05:57.583
Shule Organizatsye.

00:05:57.977 --> 00:06:05.396
zey hobn gehat di ale ovnt shuln far yugntlekhe, velkhe hobn bay tog gearbet, bay nakht hobn zikh gelernt.

00:06:06.549 --> 00:06:08.315
bloyz yidishe kinder?

00:06:08.422 --> 00:06:10.138
bloyz yidishe kinder.

00:06:10.143 --> 00:06:13.175
un vi alt hostu geven ven du host geganen dortn?

00:06:13.248 --> 00:06:17.709
ven ikh bin dortn gegangen bin ikh alt geven draytsn, fertsn yor,

00:06:17.709 --> 00:06:19.300
fuftsn yor.

00:06:20.808 --> 00:06:23.688
un ale mol ir hot geven in di zelbe ort?

00:06:23.762 --> 00:06:25.033
yo, dos zelbe ort.

00:06:25.033 --> 00:06:27.890
⟨Tvarde⟩ tsvey un tsvontsik.

00:06:28.773 --> 00:06:30.168
du host geglaykht dos?

00:06:30.292 --> 00:06:31.181
vos?

00:06:30.832 --> 00:06:32.598
t dos geglaykht?

00:06:33.549 --> 00:06:37.273
du host dos geglaykht, tsu geyn tsum shule?

00:06:37.130 --> 00:06:37.750
yo.

00:06:37.700 --> 00:06:38.454
yo?

00:06:40.873 --> 00:06:41.610
nu!

00:06:42.189 --> 00:06:43.905
vu hostu gevoynt?

00:06:44.332 --> 00:06:46.621
Tvarde zeks un fertsik.

00:06:48.737 --> 00:06:50.778
konst zogn mir vi,

00:06:49.884 --> 00:06:53.624
Varshe, oyf Tvarde zeks un fertsik.

00:06:53.630 --> 00:06:55.481
konst zogn mir vi,

00:06:55.622 --> 00:06:56.578
vu gefi-

00:06:55.790 --> 00:07:00.021
di hoyz vi vi iz es geven vi, vifl shtiber,

00:06:59.030 --> 00:07:01.466
oh, Tvarde zeks un fertsik

00:07:01.477 --> 00:07:04.242
iz gevezn a yidishe gas,

00:07:04.278 --> 00:07:08.002
kimat bloyz yidn hobn dortn gevoynt.

00:07:09.712 --> 00:07:13.217
vifl shloftsimer geven dortn

00:07:13.290 --> 00:07:14.685
bay dir in hoyz.

00:07:14.589 --> 00:07:16.232
bay mir in hoyz?

00:07:16.232 --> 00:07:19.427
oh! se geven efsher fertsik voynungen!

00:07:19.719 --> 00:07:21.840
in dayne voynungen.

00:07:21.575 --> 00:07:23.611
iz geven a tsimer,

00:07:23.735 --> 00:07:24.956
a kikh,

00:07:24.956 --> 00:07:26.700
mit tsvey tsimern.

00:07:26.756 --> 00:07:27.729
mer nisht.

00:07:29.017 --> 00:07:32.944
un du host geshlofn mit da- dayn shvester?

00:07:33.287 --> 00:07:35.441
tsuzamen nisht, bazunder.

00:07:36.341 --> 00:07:38.259
di ts- mir hobn gehat azoy.

00:07:38.433 --> 00:07:39.828
der tate

00:07:40.172 --> 00:07:44.351
iz geshtorbn in yor toyznt nayn hundert nayntsn.

00:07:45.302 --> 00:07:48.185
un di mame mit di tsvey shvestern

00:07:48.187 --> 00:07:50.817
mit mir hobn gevoynt tsuzamen

00:07:50.817 --> 00:07:53.565
Tvarde zeks un fertsik.

00:07:57.806 --> 00:08:00.281
dayn mame hot gekokht in der heym?

00:08:00.152 --> 00:08:01.564
avade.

00:08:01.333 --> 00:08:02.424
un vashn?

00:08:02.244 --> 00:08:03.709
in Varshe.

00:08:03.709 --> 00:08:06.474
opgebrente zup hot zi gekokht.

00:08:08.589 --> 00:08:11.587
vos gedenkst vos z- vos zi hot gekokhn?

00:08:12.032 --> 00:08:15.739
ikh hob dir gezogt vos iz, veyst nisht vos dos iz opgebrente zup?

00:08:15.812 --> 00:08:16.920
un vos nokh?

00:08:17.404 --> 00:08:18.104
okh!

00:08:18.140 --> 00:08:23.197
mir zenen geven in a groyse oremkeyt, vayl der tate iz geshtorbn.

00:08:23.810 --> 00:08:27.314
di kinder hobn zikh gelernt in a shule,

00:08:27.422 --> 00:08:30.589
zey hobn nokh nisht gearbet un nisht fardint,

00:08:30.662 --> 00:08:34.177
nor di eyntsike vos hot fardint iz geven di mame,

00:08:34.177 --> 00:08:36.225
velkhe hot farkoyft broyt.

00:08:38.323 --> 00:08:40.832
ikh hob ir geholfn trogn, shlepn.

00:08:43.588 --> 00:08:46.350
dayn foter, vos iz geshen mit dayn foter?

00:08:46.845 --> 00:08:48.308
oy! a groyse!

00:08:49.612 --> 00:08:51.294
me hot im geharget.

00:08:52.127 --> 00:08:55.615
in yor toyznt nayn hundert nayntsn.

00:08:55.687 --> 00:08:57.065
vos iz geshen?

00:08:59.940 --> 00:09:01.757
konkurents.

00:09:03.956 --> 00:09:06.347
konkurents iz gevezn

00:09:06.470 --> 00:09:07.713
un me hot im,

00:09:08.276 --> 00:09:12.000
vayl er hot gehat a bekeray, er hot gebakn broyt,

00:09:12.191 --> 00:09:14.298
hobn zey im gevolt likvidirn

00:09:14.298 --> 00:09:18.294
tsulib konkurentsine momentn.

00:09:19.869 --> 00:09:21.956
un zey hobn im geharget,

00:09:22.097 --> 00:09:25.148
er hot nokh ge- UNK zey hobn im tseklapt, tseshlogn,

00:09:25.148 --> 00:09:28.604
er hot nokh gelebt a tsvey vokhn, nakher iz er geshtorbn.

00:09:28.053 --> 00:09:29.448
ver hot dos gemakht?

00:09:30.568 --> 00:09:32.469
banditn. merder.

00:09:36.963 --> 00:09:39.121
du host gehat a sakh

00:09:39.121 --> 00:09:42.496
m- mentshn fun di familye vos hobn gevoynt

00:09:42.496 --> 00:09:43.911
noent tsu dir?

00:09:43.612 --> 00:09:44.318
yo.

00:09:44.318 --> 00:09:46.981
se geven. me hot gehat a familye.

00:09:47.443 --> 00:09:48.720
kuzinke?

00:09:48.624 --> 00:09:53.293
kuzinen, kuzinkes, un azoy vayter. feters, mumes.

00:09:54.632 --> 00:09:57.242
vos gedenkst du fun dayn

00:09:57.382 --> 00:09:58.811
baha- in der heym?

00:10:00.217 --> 00:10:02.236
vos heyst vos ikh gedenk?

00:10:02.968 --> 00:10:07.386
me hot gevoynt in a shtub, me hot shver un biter gearbet,

00:10:07.406 --> 00:10:09.290
me zol hobn tsu esn.

00:10:09.448 --> 00:10:13.335
di mame hot farkoyft broyt, un ikh hob getrogn di zek

00:10:13.335 --> 00:10:16.187
mit di koyshn broyt, ir geholfn.

00:10:16.215 --> 00:10:17.694
n dem hot men gelebt.

00:10:17.919 --> 00:10:20.546
vos, vu hostu genumen di broyt?

00:10:21.294 --> 00:10:22.875
in a bekeray.

00:10:23.876 --> 00:10:28.038
zi hot genu- du host genemt di broyt tsu andere mentshn?

00:10:26.981 --> 00:10:32.173
genumen broyt gekoyft in a bekeray un funander getrogn

00:10:32.246 --> 00:10:35.244
in di shtibn arayn tsu farshidene mentshn.

00:10:35.570 --> 00:10:36.999
vi alt hostu geven?

00:10:37.258 --> 00:10:38.214
ikh?

00:10:38.777 --> 00:10:41.356
elef yor, tsvelef yor,

00:10:41.356 --> 00:10:42.993
draytsn yor.

00:10:42.993 --> 00:10:46.562
un nakher hob ikh ongehoybn zikh lernen a fakh.

00:10:46.562 --> 00:10:47.934
shnayderay.

00:10:48.193 --> 00:10:49.554
vi alt host geven?

00:10:49.847 --> 00:10:53.858
tsvelef yor hob ikh ongehoybn zikh lernen shnayderay.

00:10:53.745 --> 00:10:55.123
vu hostu gelernt?

00:10:56.090 --> 00:11:03.138
in Varhse oyf Videk tsvey un tsvontsik, bay a yid velkher hot geheysn Leyvi.

00:11:03.667 --> 00:11:05.049
deys gedenk ikh.

00:11:06.452 --> 00:11:08.555
du host geglaykht makhn dos?

00:11:08.426 --> 00:11:09.298
vos?

00:11:08.848 --> 00:11:10.412
du host dos geglaykht?

00:11:11.497 --> 00:11:13.955
du host dos geglaykht?

00:11:14.484 --> 00:11:17.296
ikh hob gelernt zikh oyf shnayderay,

00:11:18.197 --> 00:11:20.115
nor ikh hob gornisht fardint.

00:11:20.812 --> 00:11:23.844
iz di mame gekumen a mol tsun im, gezogt,

00:11:24.069 --> 00:11:25.785
"mister Leyvi,

00:11:25.908 --> 00:11:28.985
far vos gebstu im nisht keyn mitog tsu esn?

00:11:29.030 --> 00:11:33.125
se hot zikh shoyn geendikt," zogt zi, "di tsayt fun shklafntum!"

00:11:34.700 --> 00:11:37.377
hot er mir ongehoybn tsu gebn mitog.

00:11:37.670 --> 00:11:42.857
ven ikh bin avek fun im, hob ikh gearbet bay farshidene shnayder varshtatn

00:11:42.868 --> 00:11:45.107
un fardint a por groshn.

00:11:45.770 --> 00:11:48.610
du host fardint gornisht fun der JOB?

00:11:47.981 --> 00:11:52.560
ven ikh bin geven bay im hob ikh nor gelernt zikh dos fakh.

00:11:52.560 --> 00:11:55.553
er hot gornisht gevolt gebn keyn groshn,

00:11:55.828 --> 00:11:59.096
un er hot nisht, farshteystu mikh, gegebn keyn esn.

00:12:00.553 --> 00:12:02.606
dayn shvester hobn gearbet?

00:12:02.814 --> 00:12:04.212
di shvester

00:12:04.212 --> 00:12:08.591
hobn gearbet shpeter in a fabrik velkhe hot oysgearbet

00:12:08.591 --> 00:12:10.369
khemishe zakhn.

00:12:13.547 --> 00:12:16.309
vos gedenkstu fun kheyder?

00:12:16.736 --> 00:12:18.401
fun vos? fun kheyder?

00:12:17.393 --> 00:12:18.468
fun kheyder.

00:12:18.660 --> 00:12:20.004
ah!.

00:12:20.820 --> 00:12:25.995
ye. me hot gelernt toyre un neviim ksuvim.

00:12:29.966 --> 00:12:34.297
me hot gelernt, farshteystu mikh, khumesh un rashe.

00:12:36.868 --> 00:12:41.705
toyre nokh nisht gelernt vayl me iz geven gelernt vayl me iz geven tsu yung.

00:12:42.555 --> 00:12:44.355
du host ge- dos geglaykht?

00:12:44.158 --> 00:12:44.844
yo.

00:12:45.828 --> 00:12:47.156
dos hot men gelernt.

00:12:47.567 --> 00:12:49.924
tu geganen tsum kheyder?

00:12:49.642 --> 00:12:52.770
oh! kheyder bin ikh gelernt efsher a

00:12:52.798 --> 00:12:54.362
a zeks yor.

00:12:54.958 --> 00:12:58.429
ongehoybn bay finef yor lernen in kheyder.

00:13:00.543 --> 00:13:01.730
un shpeter

00:13:01.742 --> 00:13:03.812
du host geganen tsum andere.

00:13:02.653 --> 00:13:06.464
shpeter der tate iz geshtorbn, ven der tate iz avek,

00:13:06.464 --> 00:13:11.642
hob ikh ongehoybn tsu helfn di mamen, un shpeter gelernt zikh shnayderay.

00:13:12.305 --> 00:13:14.662
un du host geganen tsum andern SCHOOLe.

00:13:14.364 --> 00:13:20.605
andert. nor gega- far azoy vi ikh hob gearbet bay tog, bin ikh gegangen in di

00:13:14.921 --> 00:13:16.411
vos iz di nomen f-

00:13:20.605 --> 00:13:22.208
ovnt kursn.

00:13:22.208 --> 00:13:24.315
in di andere shuln bay nakht.

00:13:24.776 --> 00:13:27.555
di andere S- shule hot gehat a nomen?

00:13:28.404 --> 00:13:29.428
dem nomen?

00:13:30.547 --> 00:13:31.807
d- gedenkst di nomen?

00:13:30.817 --> 00:13:34.676
zey hobn gehat a nomen, hobn gehat a nomen. ovnt kursn,

00:13:35.762 --> 00:13:39.840
di ver se hot dos organizirt iz gevezn

00:13:39.913 --> 00:13:43.215
Yidishe Shule Organizatsye.

00:13:43.322 --> 00:13:46.365
dos iz gevezn shuln organizirt

00:13:46.365 --> 00:13:48.699
fun di Bundishe partey.

00:13:50.763 --> 00:13:53.019
un vos hostu gelernt dortn?

00:13:52.974 --> 00:13:54.133
oh!

00:13:54.341 --> 00:13:57.373
dortn hot men shoyn gelernt geshikhte,

00:13:58.290 --> 00:13:59.981
yidishe geshikhte.

00:14:01.479 --> 00:14:08.122
shraybn, leyenen. un me hot gelernt hoykhe veltlekhe geshikhte.

00:14:08.280 --> 00:14:12.729
veltlekhe visnshaftn. veltlekhe. nisht keyn religyeze.

00:14:13.022 --> 00:14:14.116
dos iz geven

00:14:14.116 --> 00:14:18.399
fortgeshritene, progresive shuln.

00:14:18.675 --> 00:14:22.517
di vos, nor ikh hob dortn gelernt, nisht bay tog, nor bay nakht.

00:14:22.826 --> 00:14:24.542
vayl ikh hob gearbet bay tog.

00:14:25.610 --> 00:14:30.012
vos hostu geglaykht tsu tun, ven host nisht geganen tsum arbet,

00:14:30.012 --> 00:14:32.237
ven host nisht geganen tsu shule?

00:14:33.508 --> 00:14:35.966
bin ikh geven arbets-loz,

00:14:37.490 --> 00:14:39.470
veyst vos se taytsh arbets-loz?

00:14:39.515 --> 00:14:41.433
ikh hob nisht gehat keyn arbet,

00:14:43.818 --> 00:14:46.954
hob ikh ongehoybn tsu arbetn in a

00:14:46.954 --> 00:14:52.234
shekht-hoyz in Varshe.

00:14:52.408 --> 00:14:53.601
vu iz es geven?

00:14:53.724 --> 00:14:56.553
in Prage iz geven a shekht-hoyz,

00:14:56.728 --> 00:14:58.666
un a feter mayns,

00:14:58.666 --> 00:15:02.488
iz geven der eygntimer fun a groysn monopol

00:15:02.488 --> 00:15:05.109
fun kishkes, veyst vos kishkes?

00:15:06.347 --> 00:15:11.744
ven ikh bin gekumen dortn arbet tsun im, "feter, ikh arbet nisht, ikh zukh arbet."

00:15:11.744 --> 00:15:13.580
zogt er, "kum arbetn!"

00:15:14.565 --> 00:15:17.833
un ven ikh hob opgearbet a vokh tsayt,

00:15:18.024 --> 00:15:22.237
hot er aroysgenumen tsen zlotes un er hot mir gegebn.

00:15:22.935 --> 00:15:26.383
zog ikh, "feter, far tsen zlotes kon men lebn?"

00:15:26.394 --> 00:15:30.033
zogt er, "un az ikh vel dir gebn hundert, vestu nisht ganvenen?!"

00:15:32.486 --> 00:15:34.489
zog ikh, "ikh bin nisht keyn ganev!

00:15:34.663 --> 00:15:37.644
ikh bin a bavustziniker arbeter klas!"

00:15:39.523 --> 00:15:43.365
du host geglaykht leyenen o zingen, vos?

00:15:45.665 --> 00:15:48.666
shpeter hob ikh zikh ongehoybn tsu lernen

00:15:48.669 --> 00:15:51.822
in a untererdishe shule,

00:15:51.858 --> 00:15:53.416
velkhe iz gevezn

00:15:53.416 --> 00:15:55.804
oyf aza hoykhe madreyge

00:15:55.804 --> 00:15:57.709
vi universitetn.

00:15:58.777 --> 00:16:04.020
dos hot organizirt di komunistishe partey far yunge mentshn,

00:16:04.194 --> 00:16:07.229
velkher hobn nisht gehat keyn meglekhkeyt tsu lernen

00:16:07.248 --> 00:16:12.727
in di universitetn, hot men geshafn a untererdish universitet.

00:16:13.104 --> 00:16:15.933
un dortn zenen gevorn dertsoygn

00:16:16.108 --> 00:16:19.849
yunge mentshn zoln zayn gute komunistn.

00:16:19.922 --> 00:16:22.178
un me hot gelernt geshikhte,

00:16:23.769 --> 00:16:29.889
geshikhte fun literatur, ekonomye,

00:16:31.039 --> 00:16:35.722
politishe bavegungen, un politishe geshikhte.

00:16:35.722 --> 00:16:42.326
a untererdishe, ikh hob geendikt aza min universitet, a untererdishn.

00:16:42.551 --> 00:16:44.134
nisht keyn legaln.

00:16:44.134 --> 00:16:45.814
tsvey yor tsayt,

00:16:45.842 --> 00:16:46.748
un azoy vayter.

00:16:46.719 --> 00:16:49.827
un vi alt hostu geven ven du host geganen dortn?

00:16:49.284 --> 00:16:52.940
ven ikh bin alt geven shoyn akhtsn yor,

00:16:53.300 --> 00:16:57.179
ven ikh hob geendikt di untererdishn universitet

00:16:57.179 --> 00:16:58.138
in Varshe.

00:16:59.156 --> 00:17:03.555
un vi lang host geven oyfn unsh- untererdishe shule?

00:17:03.847 --> 00:17:05.124
di velkhe shule?

00:17:04.674 --> 00:17:05.785
vi lang

00:17:05.785 --> 00:17:06.992
hostu geven

00:17:06.992 --> 00:17:09.525
bay untererdishe shule?

00:17:08.774 --> 00:17:10.068
tsvey yor.

00:17:09.821 --> 00:17:10.659
tsvey yor.

00:17:10.412 --> 00:17:11.064
yo,

00:17:13.820 --> 00:17:15.266
du host geglaykht dos?

00:17:15.204 --> 00:17:16.059
vos?

00:17:15.726 --> 00:17:17.745
du host dos de- geglaykht,

00:17:18.139 --> 00:17:19.821
tsu geyn tsum shule?

00:17:20.483 --> 00:17:21.391
ikh farshtey nisht.

00:17:21.887 --> 00:17:24.362
du host dos geglaykht,

00:17:24.452 --> 00:17:27.771
tsu geyn tsu dem untererdishe shule?

00:17:26.578 --> 00:17:27.433
yo.

00:17:27.692 --> 00:17:29.461
ava- dos iz shoyn geven

00:17:29.461 --> 00:17:34.810
vayl ikh bin geven a mitglid in di yugnt komunistishe organizatsye,

00:17:34.813 --> 00:17:38.891
un zey hobn mikh dortn arayngeshikt, un dortn hob ikh gelernt.

00:17:40.145 --> 00:17:41.776
se geven yidishe?

00:17:41.816 --> 00:17:45.776
nisht bloyz keyn yidishe, alts iz geven in di poylishe shprakh,

00:17:47.064 --> 00:17:49.218
geven yidn un polakn.

00:17:49.629 --> 00:17:51.868
meydlekh un mener

00:17:51.941 --> 00:17:54.250
hobn gelernt dortn in di shule.

00:17:54.250 --> 00:17:57.335
un dos iz forgekumen umlegal, untererdish.

00:17:58.455 --> 00:18:01.993
vi- vifl kinder hobn do gelernt?

00:18:01.897 --> 00:18:05.300
oh! hobn zikh gelernt UNK zekhtsik kinder.

00:18:05.728 --> 00:18:08.307
zekhtsik yunge mentshn

00:18:08.343 --> 00:18:10.582
hobn gelernt di visnshaft

00:18:11.398 --> 00:18:13.757
der marksistisher visnshaft,

00:18:14.289 --> 00:18:15.780
der ekonomye,

00:18:16.106 --> 00:18:18.733
historishe materyalizm,

00:18:19.160 --> 00:18:20.167
farshteyst?

00:18:19.970 --> 00:18:23.255
un ver hot geven dayn TEACHERS?

00:18:23.717 --> 00:18:29.145
dos zenen geven di greste profesorn fun Varsheve Universitet,

00:18:30.652 --> 00:18:33.138
nor zey zenen geven komunistn,

00:18:33.183 --> 00:18:34.809
hobn zey undz gelernt

00:18:34.809 --> 00:18:37.785
in umlegal, untererdish.

00:18:38.634 --> 00:18:40.181
di greste gelernte.

00:18:40.659 --> 00:18:43.826
du gedenkst a nomen fun a profesor?

00:18:43.376 --> 00:18:44.147
ikh gedenk nisht.

00:18:44.540 --> 00:18:45.311
neyn.

00:18:46.397 --> 00:18:49.608
vos hostu geglaykht tsu tuen

00:18:49.608 --> 00:18:51.926
ven du hot nisht gelernt,

00:18:51.982 --> 00:18:54.407
ven du hot nisht gearbet,

00:18:54.682 --> 00:18:55.925
vos hostu gemakht?

00:18:55.796 --> 00:18:58.845
oh! hob ikh farshidene arbetn gemakht.

00:18:59.677 --> 00:19:03.080
ikh hob dir gezogt, ikh hob gearbet a tsayt in shekht-hoyz,

00:19:03.137 --> 00:19:07.401
shpeter hob ikh dortn zikh gedreyt bay tekhnishe arbetn,

00:19:07.541 --> 00:19:11.653
farrokhtn mashinen, velkhn me hot gebakn matses,

00:19:11.861 --> 00:19:13.053
un azoy vayter.

00:19:13.683 --> 00:19:16.254
oder faktish bin ikh geven fun fakh

00:19:16.254 --> 00:19:18.824
an oysgebildeter shnayder.

00:19:19.893 --> 00:19:22.689
vos, hostu geglaykht tsu zingen?

00:19:23.268 --> 00:19:24.393
zingen?

00:19:23.808 --> 00:19:24.950
zi- yo.

00:19:26.441 --> 00:19:29.827
oykhet hob ikh gehert in a dram-krayz.

00:19:30.457 --> 00:19:34.673
der firer fun dram-kray iz geven a geviser Diner,

00:19:34.673 --> 00:19:36.510
mister Diner.

00:19:37.511 --> 00:19:42.214
dortn hot men gelernt ⟨dramaturge⟩, zingen,

00:19:42.911 --> 00:19:44.807
shpiln in teater.

00:19:44.852 --> 00:19:49.166
etlekhene yor, biz tsu der milkhome iz oysgebrokhn,

00:19:49.712 --> 00:19:54.499
bin ikh gevezn tetik in dem azoy-gerufenem dram-krayz.

00:19:54.774 --> 00:19:56.692
veyst vos iz a dram-krayz? shoyn.

00:19:59.027 --> 00:20:00.231
in der heym,

00:20:00.231 --> 00:20:02.058
du host geven RELIGIOUS?

00:20:02.655 --> 00:20:03.358
neyn.

00:20:02.857 --> 00:20:04.218
yidishkeyt?

00:20:03.785 --> 00:20:07.559
neh. yidishkeyt iz geven, ober nisht keyn religye.

00:20:07.835 --> 00:20:10.648
me hot gegesn kosher esn,

00:20:11.413 --> 00:20:15.924
me hot nisht getort esn UNK, fleysh mit puter hot men nisht getort esn.

00:20:15.924 --> 00:20:16.892
ir veyst dokh.

00:20:18.382 --> 00:20:21.414
traditsye. se geven traditsye.

00:20:21.943 --> 00:20:24.030
host geganen in shul arayn?

00:20:24.407 --> 00:20:25.855
zeltns.

00:20:25.855 --> 00:20:27.905
ikh hob nor gezungen

00:20:27.950 --> 00:20:29.379
in a shul.

00:20:29.790 --> 00:20:32.586
in Varshe iz geven a Nozhik shul,

00:20:32.945 --> 00:20:42.018
dortn iz geven a groyse khor, prekhtik, un ikh hob zikh dortn arayn gekrign, ikh hob oykh mit gezungen a yor tsayt

00:20:42.497 --> 00:20:43.571
in khor.

00:20:43.796 --> 00:20:45.292
nakher bin ikh avek.

00:20:47.728 --> 00:20:50.304
du host gehat a shabes un a yontev in der heym?

00:20:50.816 --> 00:20:53.747
me hot gemakht a bisl traditsye.

00:20:54.005 --> 00:20:56.863
mit di an- gantse familye, mit,

00:20:56.098 --> 00:20:57.369
gantse famil-

00:20:56.863 --> 00:20:57.948
onkls?

00:20:57.369 --> 00:21:00.767
di mame mit di tsvey shvestern un ikh.

00:21:00.587 --> 00:21:02.471
nisht mit di kuzinke?

00:21:01.802 --> 00:21:04.530
neh, dos hot men nisht gehat keyn farbindung.

00:21:06.375 --> 00:21:09.879
nor di mame, di tsvey shvestern un ikh.

00:21:10.931 --> 00:21:15.769
du host geganen mit bloyz yidn, ober mit polakn, mit andere mentshn?

00:21:15.015 --> 00:21:17.777
ikh hob gehat fraynt polakn oykh.

00:21:18.120 --> 00:21:19.464
di gantse tsayt.

00:21:19.014 --> 00:21:19.737
yo.

00:21:19.757 --> 00:21:25.185
vayl me iz geven tsuzamen in der erdishn universitet, geven polakn, yidn,

00:21:26.372 --> 00:21:29.946
un ikh hob gehat polakn in di tsayt fun der okupatsye,

00:21:29.946 --> 00:21:33.132
tsuzamen gearbet, geholfn hobn zey,

00:21:35.231 --> 00:21:36.440
mit polakn.

00:21:37.273 --> 00:21:39.852
un vu hostu ahin gekumen

00:21:39.852 --> 00:21:40.847
tsu di

00:21:40.850 --> 00:21:42.886
untererdishe shule?

00:21:43.652 --> 00:21:51.960
bay yidn iz geven kinder velkhe zenen alt gevorn tsvelef yor, hobn gehert in an organizatsye

00:21:51.971 --> 00:21:55.324
velkhe hot zikh geheysn Pyanir, Pyanir.

00:21:56.460 --> 00:22:01.216
fun di di organizatsye Pyanir zenen zey ibergegangen

00:22:01.235 --> 00:22:05.044
tsu di komunistishe yugnt organizatsye.

00:22:06.298 --> 00:22:09.434
fun di yugnt organizatsye zenen zey gevorn

00:22:09.434 --> 00:22:14.494
fulshtendike mitglider fun di komunistishe partey.

00:22:15.123 --> 00:22:19.238
un di komunistishe partey in Poyln hot ekzistirt

00:22:19.258 --> 00:22:22.672
fun yor toyznt nayn hundert tsvontsik,

00:22:22.672 --> 00:22:24.782
biz akht un draysik.

00:22:24.782 --> 00:22:32.668
Stalin hot funandergelozt der partey, bashuldikt az zey zenen farreter, agentn fun di politsey.

00:22:33.045 --> 00:22:34.389
vos iz geshen?

00:22:35.171 --> 00:22:37.005
azoy hot Stalin gemakht.

00:22:37.365 --> 00:22:39.503
veyst ver der Stalin iz geven?

00:22:39.626 --> 00:22:43.007
un se gevorn in akht un draysikstn yor,

00:22:43.007 --> 00:22:51.702
hot oyfgehert tsu ekzistirn a komunistishe partey in poyln, oder zenen farshtanen farshidene grupn,

00:22:54.543 --> 00:22:57.676
velkhe zenen geven onhenger fun di bavegung.

00:22:58.070 --> 00:22:59.718
iz di ershte zakh,

00:23:00.551 --> 00:23:03.527
zey hobn geshafn meglekhkeytn

00:23:03.527 --> 00:23:06.648
far yidn, polakn, vos zenen gezitsn

00:23:06.648 --> 00:23:08.932
in di poylishe tfises.

00:23:10.237 --> 00:23:14.771
iz geven an organizatsye velkher hot geheysn MOPR:

00:23:15.215 --> 00:23:20.474
MEZHDUNARODNAYA ORGANIZATSIYA POMOSHCHI REVOLOYUTSINISTUM.

00:23:20.548 --> 00:23:24.350
a internatsyonaler organizatsye velkher hot geholfn

00:23:24.350 --> 00:23:27.849
revolutsyonern velkhe zenen gezitsn in tfise.

00:23:29.694 --> 00:23:30.532
oy vey!

00:23:33.862 --> 00:23:36.641
vos gedenkstu fun dayn muter?

00:23:38.351 --> 00:23:39.510
gornisht.

00:23:42.654 --> 00:23:45.348
ikh gedenk zi iz geven an almone,

00:23:46.417 --> 00:23:49.010
un zi iz, farshteystu mikh,

00:23:49.286 --> 00:23:50.245
UNK,

00:23:50.245 --> 00:23:54.202
ven di daytshn hobn farnumen Poyln hot zi gevoynt in Lide,

00:23:54.202 --> 00:23:56.638
un dortn hot men ir geharget.

00:23:58.263 --> 00:24:02.327
vos gedenkstu fun der heym? vos zi hot gemakht, vos zi hot getun,

00:24:02.327 --> 00:24:03.658
vos zi hot geredt?

00:24:03.731 --> 00:24:06.780
neyn, dos gedenk ikh gornisht.

00:24:07.410 --> 00:24:08.738
un dayn foter?

00:24:09.097 --> 00:24:15.656
nu, gedenk ikh nisht, vayl ikh bin alt gevezn akht, nayn oyr ven er iz geshtorbn.

00:24:16.488 --> 00:24:18.895
du host geshpilt mit dayn shvester?

00:24:19.425 --> 00:24:20.263
vos?

00:24:20.015 --> 00:24:22.862
du host geshpilt mit dayn shvester?

00:24:22.850 --> 00:24:26.273
yo, geredt, geshpilt, gezungen.

00:24:26.273 --> 00:24:29.882
un ikh bin geven a shpiler in soker oykhet.

00:24:32.334 --> 00:24:34.694
vos hostu geredt in der heym?

00:24:34.697 --> 00:24:37.054
in yidish, ober in poylish?

00:24:37.194 --> 00:24:38.370
vi hostu geredt?

00:24:38.544 --> 00:24:40.479
in yidish un poylish.

00:24:41.278 --> 00:24:42.099
beyde?

00:24:41.750 --> 00:24:43.094
beyde shprakhn.

00:24:45.885 --> 00:24:49.721
du host gehat froynt vos iz geven yidishe

00:24:49.732 --> 00:24:51.026
un polakn?

00:24:51.150 --> 00:24:52.039
beyde?

00:24:52.061 --> 00:24:54.958
yo, beyde. yidishe, poylishe fraynt.

00:24:55.807 --> 00:24:58.468
hostu ge- du host gefilt

00:24:58.625 --> 00:25:01.033
DIFFERENT tsu zayn a yid?

00:25:01.224 --> 00:25:03.227
oder du host gemeynt az di zelb-

00:25:01.967 --> 00:25:03.581
neyn, neyn.

00:25:03.840 --> 00:25:07.479
ikh hob mikh gefilt vi a frayer birger.

00:25:08.075 --> 00:25:10.989
k- se bay mir nisht geven keyn rasn-has,

00:25:11.383 --> 00:25:15.174
keyn natsyonalitetn, ale mentshn zenen brider

00:25:15.247 --> 00:25:16.558
un shvester.

00:25:18.268 --> 00:25:19.646
se hot geven

00:25:19.888 --> 00:25:23.662
antisemit- -semitizm in Varshe?

00:25:23.280 --> 00:25:26.008
avade iz geven antisemitizm.

00:25:25.558 --> 00:25:28.471
ven iz IT gev- ven hostu gefilt?

00:25:28.882 --> 00:25:31.121
oy! ikh hob shoyn derfilt

00:25:31.177 --> 00:25:33.804
bin alt gevezn tsen yor.

00:25:34.586 --> 00:25:37.247
vayl der rebe hot undz gelernt

00:25:38.670 --> 00:25:42.574
az a sh- goyishke sheygets get dir a zets,

00:25:42.602 --> 00:25:44.455
zolstu im nisht tsurikgebn,

00:25:44.455 --> 00:25:46.443
nor zogn a brokhe.

00:25:46.753 --> 00:25:47.743
herst!

00:25:48.221 --> 00:25:52.080
ikh hob gezogt di brokhe, se hot mir gornisht geholfn, ikh bin geven farblutikt.

00:25:52.828 --> 00:25:57.564
un az me hot tsurikgegebn iz gut gevezn, me hot zikh nisht badorfn lozn.

00:25:58.160 --> 00:26:00.179
der religye hot gelernt,

00:26:00.236 --> 00:26:03.707
zog brokhes, az er shlogt dikh a polak,

00:26:04.050 --> 00:26:07.216
yo! azoy hot men gelernt in kheyder!

00:26:07.779 --> 00:26:11.857
ven undz hobn gezogt, oh! di beste zakh tsuriktsugebn.

00:26:13.719 --> 00:26:17.190
avade iz gevezn in Varshe antisemitizm.

00:26:17.347 --> 00:26:20.126
dos iz geven nayntsn tsvontsik.

00:26:20.570 --> 00:26:22.218
ven dos iz geshen.

00:26:21.667 --> 00:26:23.079
oh in nayntsn,

00:26:22.359 --> 00:26:25.256
un shpeter vos iz geshen mit antisemitn?

00:26:26.173 --> 00:26:30.656
di antisemitizm bizn hayntikn tog iz er aktuel.

00:26:33.783 --> 00:26:37.642
nayntsn ts- finef un tsvontsik, nayntsn draysik,

00:26:38.053 --> 00:26:41.119
vu iz IT geshen di antisemitn in,

00:26:41.664 --> 00:26:47.947
in nayntsn draysik iz der antisemitizm geven zeyer shtark in Poyln,

00:26:47.947 --> 00:26:49.508
vayl der regirung,

00:26:51.165 --> 00:26:55.128
dos iz geven di letste yorn fun Pilsutski,

00:26:55.128 --> 00:26:58.418
bay im, er hot nokh a bisl gehaltn in ordenung,

00:26:58.438 --> 00:27:01.953
oder ven er iz geshtorbn in fir un draysikstn yor,

00:27:01.998 --> 00:27:05.351
hot zikh ongehoybn a shreklekhe antisemitizm.

00:27:05.559 --> 00:27:06.819
vos iz geshen?

00:27:09.508 --> 00:27:13.738
far vos iz geshen antisemitizm, dos iz a gantse lere.

00:27:13.760 --> 00:27:14.919
nisht far vos,

00:27:15.093 --> 00:27:17.382
vos hot geshen? vos iz,

00:27:18.941 --> 00:27:21.079
me hot bashuldikt yidn

00:27:22.400 --> 00:27:24.791
farshidene zakhn,

00:27:25.286 --> 00:27:29.972
farshteyst. zey ganvenen, zey gazlenen, zey narn op,

00:27:30.332 --> 00:27:32.739
zey nitsn oys un azoy vayter.

00:27:32.677 --> 00:27:34.190
ver hot dos gemakht?

00:27:34.365 --> 00:27:37.312
a poylisher politisher parteyen.

00:27:38.702 --> 00:27:40.164
tsu dir oykhet?

00:27:40.052 --> 00:27:40.975
ver?

00:27:40.642 --> 00:27:41.750
tsu dir?

00:27:42.161 --> 00:27:45.564
avade, ikh bin geven a yid, oykh dos zelbe.

00:27:49.198 --> 00:27:52.922
ven hot di doytshn arayngekumen tsu Varshe?

00:27:54.378 --> 00:27:56.009
dem ershtn,

00:27:58.007 --> 00:28:02.524
dem nayntn toyznt nayn hundert neyn un draysik.

00:28:03.828 --> 00:28:06.894
vu hot ir, zi, du gebe- geven?

00:28:06.039 --> 00:28:08.227
in Varshe bin ikh gevezn

00:28:08.334 --> 00:28:10.792
ven di daytshn zenen arayngekumen.

00:28:11.237 --> 00:28:13.628
un me hot gekemft gegn zey.

00:28:15.253 --> 00:28:18.369
du host geven bayn arbet, ober der, in der heym?

00:28:18.138 --> 00:28:21.139
ikh bin geven in der heym oder gearbet

00:28:21.159 --> 00:28:22.875
az di daytshn

00:28:23.387 --> 00:28:25.187
me zol zikh akegn shteln.

00:28:25.479 --> 00:28:27.920
gekemft un azoy vayter, gemakht

00:28:28.466 --> 00:28:32.915
farshidene azoy gerufene shterungen far di daytshn.

00:28:33.410 --> 00:28:36.290
vayl di daytshn hobn yetst ayngenumen Varshe,

00:28:36.870 --> 00:28:39.767
bay di ende, nokh a khoydesh kamfn.

00:28:42.050 --> 00:28:49.368
un yetst geven SPECIAL RULES? zey hobn gezogt az di yidn muz tuen dos un dos un yents?

00:28:49.965 --> 00:28:51.461
ver di daytshn?

00:28:50.977 --> 00:28:51.714
di daytshn.

00:28:52.496 --> 00:28:57.114
nokh tsvey tog hobn zey bald aroysgegebn farordenungen

00:28:57.947 --> 00:28:59.460
kegn yidn.

00:29:01.085 --> 00:29:04.677
on di farordenung hot men nisht gekont koyfn keyn shtikl broyt.

00:29:04.697 --> 00:29:05.856
gornisht.

00:29:06.114 --> 00:29:09.382
se hot zikh ongehoybn a hunger, a noyt, un azoy vayter.

00:29:09.877 --> 00:29:14.175
un shpeter hobn zey geshafn dem geto in Varshe.

00:29:14.838 --> 00:29:16.554
in nayntsn fertsik.

00:29:17.100 --> 00:29:18.411
far di geto,

00:29:18.606 --> 00:29:22.455
hot badorfn esn,

00:29:22.455 --> 00:29:24.563
vu hostu gekrign esn?

00:29:23.917 --> 00:29:26.122
se gevezn tsu esn,

00:29:27.680 --> 00:29:31.623
oder me hot gemuzt, koydem yidn hobn shoyn nisht gearbet.

00:29:31.713 --> 00:29:34.914
yidishe gesheftn zenen gevorn likvidirt,

00:29:35.763 --> 00:29:36.804
farshteyst?

00:29:38.210 --> 00:29:39.301
un vos nokh?

00:29:39.948 --> 00:29:45.444
un, farshteystu mikh, se geven zeyer biter un yidn hobn ongehoybn antloyfn

00:29:45.517 --> 00:29:48.194
keyn Sovyet Rusland, keyn Rusland.

00:29:49.787 --> 00:29:53.208
me vet vartn a minut, oystoyshn di TAPE.

00:29:53.921 --> 00:29:54.810
OKEY.
